This feeds into people's values.

07:40.000 --> 07:41.600
They see other people's fake lives

07:41.600 --> 07:43.360
and hold their own up to the same standard.

07:43.360 --> 07:45.280
These people then perpetuate the cycle,

07:45.280 --> 07:46.720
which then brings the Habitus

07:46.720 --> 07:49.280
further and further away from authenticity and truth.

07:49.280 --> 07:51.840
Corporatization of societies then also reflected

07:51.840 --> 07:53.520
in the Habitus of both the Truman Show

07:53.520 --> 07:54.800
and in our own society.

