that she has no other response.

08:20.720 --> 08:22.400
She just keeps reading the same script,

08:22.400 --> 08:24.320
but it's so much worse in our own society

08:24.320 --> 08:26.640
where our Habitus is so heavily corporatized,

08:26.640 --> 08:29.200
with corporate values being held in such a high regard

