Never before in history has this happened.

08:34.000 --> 08:36.400
Truman's suspicions of reality are then brought up again

08:36.400 --> 08:38.640
when his father, who he assumes is dead,

08:38.640 --> 08:41.120
shows up on his way to work dressed as a beggar.

08:41.120 --> 08:41.680
Dead?

