Truman's father is then quickly whisked away on a bus,

08:44.080 --> 08:45.920
but not before Truman sees his face.

08:45.920 --> 08:47.360
He realizes something is up,

08:47.360 --> 08:48.560
so he goes to talk to his mother

08:48.560 --> 08:50.720
who tries to explain away his father's reappearance

08:50.720 --> 08:53.280
by suggesting that he's just crazy and hallucinated it.

08:53.280 --> 08:54.880
This time, it doesn't convince Truman,

08:54.880 --> 08:57.920
who also notices how often his wife name drops brands.

08:57.920 --> 08:59.680
As Truman starts to go through his old things,

08:59.680 --> 09:01.840
the movie flashes back to Truman's collages

